data.description: Own your own home in the 1600 block of Westmoreland St.  3 bedroom TWO BATH home is ready to move in to.  Large backyard with room for parking at the back of the lot, if needed.  Home has been updated and is in excellent condition.  Spacious, open living and kitchen area. Separate laundry room. Refrigerator will stay.  2 car carport. Laminate flooring and carpet in bedrooms.  Flood insurance approximately $300-$400 per year, buyer must verify.
